Package: simpleshotter
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Cross-platform screenshot tool with window and control detection
 SimpleShotter is a Snipaste-like screenshot tool that supports automatic
 window region detection and UI control detection via AT-SPI.
 Features include region selection, global hotkey, clipboard copy,
 file saving, and annotation tools.
